Im funny, mature, like to have a good company and have a nice conversation. i like sport go to the gym. i dont smoke. looking for a nice girl, race doesnt matter. lets start from here and lets see where it take us) im real, not some kind of bot. if you are interested please put "real" in subject line, so i know that you are real and reply with some pictures
